  <header class="header">
    <div class="header-container">
      <h1>KI-Tools durchsuchen</h1>
      <p>Entdecke die besten KI-Tools für Textgenerierung, Bildgenerierung, Coding und mehr. Alle Tools sind getestet und kategorisiert.</p>
      
      <div class="header-stats">
        <div class="header-stat">
          <span class="header-stat-number">{tools.length}</span>
          <span class="header-stat-label">Tools</span>
        </div>
        <div class="header-stat">
          <span class="header-stat-number">{categories.length}</span>
          <span class="header-stat-label">Kategorien</span>
        </div>
        <div class="header-stat">
          <span class="header-stat-number">{freeTools}</span>
          <span class="header-stat-label">Kostenlos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="header-stat">
          <span class="header-stat-number">{freemiumTools}</span>
          <span class="header-stat-label">Freemium</span>
        </div>
      </div>
